{
  "stem": "18778.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 312.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And after about two years, I met an old friend whom I had known 40-some years ago.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was in-- in the meantime, he had lived here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He had lived in Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He's a survivor of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He has his own story to tell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we started to see each other, and we've been together, now, over seven years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "At the moment, I'm recovering from surgery, and he is a caretaker beyond description.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name is Max Percal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our first visit back to Germany was in 1963 when we had the opportunity of joining a charter trip to Dusseldorf for a printing convention, which takes place there every year, with friends of ours who are in the business.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were the only non-printers on the plane.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, I have to tell you, I was very nervous about returning to Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My nanny came to meet us at the plane, and the whole plane knew about this reunion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, everybody watched this, when she stood there with a bunch of flowers and we saw each other again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CRYING] And at that time, I-- my husband took me to his hometown, which was Andernach, a small town on the Rhine near Koblenz.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was a very tearful experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a very small town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At the time he lived there, there were just 10,000 people, and the Loeb family was very well known.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were in the distilling business, wine and distilling business, liquor distilling business, and they were well known.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had been there as a GI and arrested a few Nazis, which, meanwhile, got out again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I said, it was rather a tearful experience.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
